      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1700000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Managed Grafana → Grafana na AKS\nAMW/DCR/DCE (managed Prometheus) → Mimir (+ Prometheus scraper)\nremote_write do AMW → remote_write do Mimir\nAuth kubelet/IMDS (azuread) → Workload Identity (UAMI + fed cred)\nPE + strefa DNS → Private Endpointy + prywatne strefy DNS\nPLS + Managed Private Endpoint → prywatne wystawienie UI / cross-VNet",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Managed Grafana → Grafana na AKS\nAMW/DCR/DCE (managed Prometheus) → Mimir (+ Prometheus scraper)\nremote_write do AMW → remote_write do Mimir\nAuth kubelet/IMDS (azuread) → Workload Identity (UAMI + fed cred)\nPE + strefa DNS → Private Endpointy + prywatne strefy DNS\nPLS + Managed Private Endpoint → prywatne wystawienie UI / cross-VNet",
